<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0251b01"/><p id="pI01p0251b0101">左葙都維那王仕力金<note n="0251001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31110;＝剛【史】</note><app n="0251001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31110;</rdg></app>主王始
<lb ed="C I" n="0251b02"/>都維那曜鋒將軍諸葛元&CB00130;
<lb ed="C I" n="0251b03"/>大齋主薛文宜　大碑主諸葛惡□
